36:44.169 --> 36:45.398
This is <i>my</i> office.

36:45.470 --> 36:46.494
That's my desk.

36:46.571 --> 36:47.732
This is my chair.

36:47.806 --> 36:49.137
This is my job.

36:49.207 --> 36:50.402
You look to me like somebody

36:50.475 --> 36:52.409
