watch a baseball game with me, huh?

37:00.585 --> 37:01.575
Not tonight.

37:01.653 --> 37:02.745
Really?

37:02.821 --> 37:04.550
Yeah.

37:07.092 --> 37:10.323
All right.

37:10.395 --> 37:12.227
I'm not discouraged.

37:12.297 --> 37:13.196
Good.

37:14.933 --> 37:16.765
I am Dan.

37:16.835 --> 37:17.859
Yes, you are.

37:20.105 --> 37:23.370
See you Monday.

37:25.009 --> 37:27.239
Yeah.

