<i>Listen to what Milton</i> says
<i>in Paradise Lost</i> --

37:29.881 --> 37:33.579
he's basically saying that Orion
becomes an instrument of divine wrath,

37:33.651 --> 37:36.780
perfectly controlled by God to
thwart those who would defy him,

37:36.855 --> 37:39.051
who "treadeth upon
the waves of the sea."

