37:47.165 --> 37:48.098
-- Yes.
-- So...

37:48.166 --> 37:49.429
I want to talk to Jeremy.

37:49.501 --> 37:51.401
No problem.
Talk to me later, Jeremy.

37:51.469 --> 37:52.959
-- Thanks.
-- By the way...

37:53.037 --> 37:56.302
<i>this is the second time today
I've been kicked out of a room,</i>

37:56.374 --> 37:58.604
